nnoremap <Leader>q <Action>(CloseContent)
nnoremap <Leader>Q <Action>(CloseAllEditors)
nnoremap <Leader>w <Action>(SaveDocument)
nnoremap <Leader>W <Action>(SaveAll)

" =============================================================================
" Development & Code Tools (Leader + ;d)
